    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.00752.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Burlington <choice>
                            <abbr>Vt.</abbr>
                            <expan>Vermont</expan>
                        </choice></name>
                    <date when="1883-06-16" rend="right">Saturday afternoon June 16</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>

            <p>Are you well enough my <hi rend="underline">dear brother</hi> for me to send you my love and tell you I am so
                glad and happy&#8212;<hi rend="underline">for</hi> I know you are gaining</p>
            <p>That was a wonderful welcome <unclear reason="illegible" cert="high" resp="#ss"
                    >card</unclear> Walt dear&#8212;You <choice>
                    <orig>wont</orig>
                    <reg>won't</reg>
                </choice> have to write to me again dearest brother, <choice>
                    <orig>till</orig>
                    <reg>until</reg>
                </choice> you get stronger.&#8212;I <choice>
                        <sic>dont</sic>
                        <corr>don't</corr>
                    </choice> feel uneasy.&#8212;I know you are getting better and I <hi rend="underline"
                    >am oh so thankful</hi></p>

            <closer>
                <signed>sister Han</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
